---
title: Retro Veggie Burger with Beyond Meat® and Caramelized Onions
description: Our dinnertime creation is the Retro Burger. Caramelized onions, cheddar cheese, flavourful buns and veggie patties. This burger comes together quickly and will make your weeknights delicious!
